00:17:10.800 --> 00:17:13.600
But that little star and heart come in to pick the locks!

00:17:13.700 --> 00:17:20.100
Good work! Oh no! Little star buddy can't unlock all these doors!

00:17:20.100 --> 00:17:22.240
