00:17:22.240 --> 00:17:25.200
(as Braveheart) Well, I guess the rest of ya gotta die. Toodles!

00:17:25.200 --> 00:17:28.120
NC: No, they go to get the key from around his neck

00:17:28.120 --> 00:17:30.260
as he keeps changing shape as he snoozes.

