00:17:34.160 --> 00:17:37.800
(mockingly) but that wouldn't be caring enough.

00:17:37.800 --> 00:17:41.500
But the plan backfires as he banishes all the Care Bears into little, red crystals.

00:17:41.500 --> 00:17:44.800
The kids show up to see the evil he's done, Christy included.

